node.text: GIIIIRRRRLLLLSSS approved (Miss. Sarah had to be in the picture 😂) 🙌🏼 This summer has been all about the bug content and how to minimize them! @zevoinsect is another product without harsh chemicals that is safe around humans and pets (or chickens ) when used as directed and WORKS. It’s plant based and drives the bugs/ insects away! You can shop for it in-store and online at Home Depot, Target and Walmart. Or head to my stories for more information! #WaySmarterThanBugs # Ad

Labor of dang love I tell ya! When I realized the 71 year old floors were underneath I had to save them! They are perfectly imperfect as I ran into some bumps (couldn’t feather in the boards) but DANG! I love them! Next phase- drywall and paint 🙌🏼

Phase 2 of my patio is complete 🙌🏼 I had sooo much fun learning how to do stamped concrete! It’s a true art! I chose a subtle stamp and tan/grey colors for the tint! Next up… we’re duping a $3000 farmhouse table for under $400 🙌🏼
.
.
.

Y’all ready for this? After a cup of coffee this morning I decided it was time to remodel the bathroom (it’s not only dated but there’s no insulation) it’s been quite the day with this renovation turning into quite the project 😬😂 but truthfully, if not now then WHEN?! This is a project for sure but I’m up for it!

DIY Pergola is DONE! I have dreamed of having an outdoor patio with a pergola and it’s coming to life! I had some awesome guys from our shed shop come and help me build this and teach me things along the way! Building deets in highlights plus more info on cost, materials and my design coming soon! Now on to the concrete work! Whatcha think?!
